Package: bfsl
Title: Best-fit Straight Line
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Patrick", "Sturm", email = "sturm@tofwerk.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The bfsl package provides the best-fit straight line of bivariate 
  data with (possibly correlated) errors in both coordinates.
